<div class="container">
    <h1>Watch Our Congress! Help Keep Them Clean and Accountable!</h1>
    <p>
        They pour out so much stuff on a good day that no one in their right mind can keep up. The smallest things can
        have
        the largest impacts on our society. A little tarif increase or reduction can have wide rammifications. A new
        rule can make an
        industry completely unviable now. Find out what topics are included in every rule and browse the parts that
        matter to you the ordinary citizen.
        Inform yourself better than the average citizen with the primary source. Do your own research using the actual
        primary sources with this AI enhanced site.
    </p>
    <p>Now is the time to inform yourself and search by topics. See what was published in the past, and how trends on
        topics have changed.</p>

    <div class="row g-2 align-items-center">
        {{!-- Radio Buttons for House or Senate per bootstrap --}}
        <div class="col-auto">
            <div class="btn-group" role="group">
                <input type="radio" class="btn-check" name="btnradio" id="btnradio1" autocomplete="off" checked
                    onchange="fetchDataForChamber('H')">
                <label class="btn btn-outline-primary" for="btnradio1">House</label>

                <input type="radio" class="btn-check" name="btnradio" id="btnradio2" autocomplete="off"
                    onchange="fetchDataForChamber('S')">
                <label class="btn btn-outline-primary" for="btnradio2">Senate</label>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-auto">
            <input class="form-control-lg" type="text" id="search" placeholder="Search for your Congress Person">
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="row">


        <div id="container"></div>
        <script type="module" src="/static/viz-js/congress-network.js?cache-bust={{ CacheBust }}"></script>
        <script>
            window.onload = () => {
                fetchDataForChamber('H');
            }
        </script>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-4">
            {{> 'partials/gauge' title="Total Topics Identified" value=TotalTags titleColor="#FF0000"}}
        </div>
        <div class="col-4">
            {{> 'partials/gauge' title="Total Tags Applied" value=TotalTopics }}
        </div>
        <div class="col-4">
            {{> 'partials/gauge' title="Total Laws Indexed" value=TotalLaws }}
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr />

    <h3>
        Search Topics
        <span class="htmx-indicator">
            <img src="/static/img/bars.svg" /> Searching...
        </span>
    </h3>
    <p>Search for the topics most important to you!</p>
    <input class="form-control-lg" style="width:100%" type="search" name="search"
        placeholder="Begin Typing To Search Tags and Topics..." hx-get="/htmx/topic-search"
        hx-trigger="input changed delay:350ms, search" hx-target="#search-results" hx-indicator=".htmx-indicator">


    <div id="search-results"></div>

    <hr />

    <h3>Recent Laws</h3>
    {{> 'partials/law-list' }}

</div>